SchedleTask support adding linked_list by default

--------
In cfs and fifo scheduling, task is already a ListNode.
In addition, in most scheduling scenarios, tasks will be
added to the linked list (wait queue) as list nodes.
Therefore, it is decided to make Node support as the
default behavior of Task.

Signed-off-by: guoweikang <guoweikang.kernel@gmail.com>
